	- No functional changes.

	- Use Complete::Dist.

	- Replace App::PMUtils with depending on Complete::Module directly.


0.03    2014-12-12 (PERLANCAR)

        - Add utility: uninstall-dist.


0.02    2014-12-06 (PERLANCAR)

